com.isotrol.impe3.pms.gui.client.util
Class PmsChangeEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.data.ChangeEvent
      com.isotrol.impe3.pms.gui.client.util.PmsChangeEvent

public class PmsChangeEvent
extends com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.data.ChangeEvent

ChangeEvent can only provide information about involved Models.
PMS services don't work always with Models, so some extra event info must be supplied when firing events.
This class offers an additional property where anything can be inserted.
It also defines additional event types.

Author:
Andrei Cojocaru
